'''Christiane Chabi-Kao''' (wavutse ku ya 30 Kamena 1963) ni umuyobozi wa filime wo muri [[Bene|Bénine]] akaba n'umwanditsi.<ref>http://africultures.com/personnes?no=10095</ref>

== Ubuzima ==
Chabi-Kao yavukiye i Marseille mu [[Bufaransa]] mu 1963.  Yize muri Kaminuza ya Reims Champagne-Ardenne kuva 1984 kugeza 1986<ref>https://copainsdavant.linternaute.com/p/christiane-chabi-kao-2870640</ref>. Mu 1990, Chabi-Kao yasubiye muri [[Afurika]].  Yasohokanye na filime ye ya mbere, ''Les enfants esclaves'', mu 2005, documentaire isobanura abana b'abacakara bigezweho<ref>https://www.expatica.com/es/uncategorized/benin-filmmaker-takes-fight-against-child-labour-to-school-37507/</ref>. 

Mu 2007, yayoboye filime ''Les inseparables''. Ivuga amateka y'abavandimwe Yawa na Abi, se bamugurisha ku mucuruza w'abana, maze nyina ajya mu ishami rishinzwe kurengera abana rya Polisi kugira ngo amenye uko byagenze.<ref>https://www.allocine.fr/personne/fichepersonne_gen_cpersonne=430660.html</ref> Iyi filime yakozwe na UNICEF na Radiyo na Televiziyo y'igihugu ya [[Bénin]] (ORTB), isohoka nk'uruhererekane rwa firime enye<ref>http://africanwomenincinema.blogspot.com/2013/12/christiane-chabi-kao-festival_1.html</ref>. Chabi-Kao yanditse iyi filime mu rwego rwo gukangurira no guhagarika icuruzwa ry'abana.<ref>Christiane Chabi-Kao - AlloCiné (allocine.fr)</ref>  Yakiriye igihembo nyafurika Numerique mu iserukiramuco rya Vues d'Afrique ryabereye i Montreal mu 2008, anahabwa igihembo cy’uburenganzira bwa muntu mu iserukiramuco rya Filimi na Televiziyo rya Panafrican 2009 rya Ouagadougou. <ref>https://www.europeana.eu/en/item/2022116/urn_axmedis_00000_obj_c547dc82_3292_491a_b7c0_d0b57fd3ea50</ref> Nyuma yo kumenyeshwa itegeko ribuza kwerekanwa ku buntu, Chabi-Kao yateguye kwerekana filime ku banyeshuri 300 ba Burkinabe<ref>https://www.telerama.fr/personnalite/christiane-chabi-kao,94457,filmographie.php</ref>. 

Mu 2009, yasimbuye Monique Mbeke Phoba nk'umuyobozi w'ikirori cya Lagunimages i Cotonou .  Nkumuyobozi, Chabi-Kao afasha kwambara iserukiramuco rya firime ryizina rimwe.<ref>https://www.allmovie.com/movie/les-insparables-v515131/corrections</ref>  Yakoreye iserukiramuco imyaka itari mike mbere yo kuba umuyobozi, ahabwa inkunga na Deutsche Welle Academy yo kwiga uko bategura ibirori<ref>https://www.senscritique.com/liste/Les_meilleurs_films_avec_Dragon_Ball_Z_Univers_2_Christiane/3045166</ref>. Chabi-Kao yanditse akanayobora ibiganiro bya televiziyo ''bigizwe n'ibice 14'' muri Les Chenapans muri 2013. Irerekana ubuzima nintambara byingimbi batanu bo muri Bénin, kandi ikoresha abakinnyi badafite umwuga<ref>https://www.filmstarts.de/personen/430660.html</ref>. 

